    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is essentially in brand-new condition, offering a premium driving experience for the most discerning buyer.",
