    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade specimen preserved in pristine condition. This vehicle exemplifies automotive excellence, having been maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. With flawless aesthetics and mechanical integrity that commands respect, it offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a benchmark example of its class. An uncompromising choice for those who seek the pinnacle of pre-owned luxury.",
      "price": 48950.0,
